reviewText:
Lacklustre even for hardcore Formula 1 fans:
1. Lack of many real F1 elements (safety car, vitual safety car, etc);
2. Lack of gameplay modes (scenario mode, career mode);
3. Bugs and creepy Maldonado-esque AIs;
4. 2014 contents feel redundant.

